data.description: West Palmdale Beauty up for sale!! Freshly painted, whole house water softener, Vera smart home (light switches and fans can be controlled by Alex, Google or Veraapp-Zwave), Nest thermostats, Schlage Smart locks, Ring smoke & security with front and backyard cameras installed, GW security camera system with 15 cameras (a capacity for 16), dual pane windows (4) newer down stairs (1) upstairs along with the down stairs glass door slider, wood flooring with sound dampening underlayment in master bedroom, wood flooring with premium underlayment in living room and entry way. Appliances included: Maytag washer, Whirlpool gas dryer,  28 cu. Ft Samsung Refrigerator (stainless steel) GE Café convection /convention/self clean oven (gas) The location is highly desirable with convenient access to shopping, dining, and recreational activities. The highly regarded local school districts provide excellent educational opportunities. The community is known for its serene and welcoming atmosphere, offering a sense of inclusivity and belonging. This is a rare opportunity to own a home with lots of amenities in a peaceful community. Don't miss out on this exceptional property - schedule a showing today and experience the best of Palmdale living! Property may qualify for a Grant of up to 15K this is a gift not a loan see attached flyer for more information.
